-- Features: acid detection, trajectory prediction, slide prediction, safe-path sweep,
--           robust redirect application (AssemblyLinearVelocity + Velocity + impulses),
--           optional debug arc drawing.
-- Usage: require this module as a LocalScript and call returned controller methods.

